    "where s max is the maximum size of any Sepset.",
    "This complexity bound is hard to quantify, but PC is polynomial given a limit on node degree (Claassen et al. 2013).",
    "Although far more efficient, the PC algorithm is less stable than SGS.",
    "For example, edges mistakenly removed in the adjacency phase can result in other edges being mistakenly retained later on in the adjacency phase."
